    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >活出夜晚的精彩!</h2> <br><strong>自己当老板开夜店，打造全城第一的娱乐场所。</strong> 选择喜欢的角色，进入以第一人称视角呈现的醉人夜店世界。夜晚用心经营自己的娱乐场所，白天为下一个夜晚做准备。竞争永远不会休止，所以，务必尽一切努力赢得顾客的赞叹，增加回头客。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621900/extras/e620823f19a4c0bf65c1a3e5c010b1fa.poster.avif?t=1765282542\" width=600 height=199 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621900/extras/e620823f19a4c0bf65c1a3e5c010b1fa.webm?t=1765282542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >这是你的酒吧。 </h2> 气氛由你来营造。从挑选嗨曲到装饰会所，再到雇佣合适的保镖、调酒师和舞者，所有的一切，你都可以全权作主。结交生意伙伴，备足货品，在顾客间发生冲突时及时介入。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621900/extras/7177d17d218993afebd9246afc89d1e1.poster.avif?t=1765282542\" width=600 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621900/extras/7177d17d218993afebd9246afc89d1e1.webm?t=1765282542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>在这个世界里，每个 NPC 都有存在的意义。与他们交谈。获取他们的反馈。领会他们的言外之意，探索如何改善你的会所，让顾客满意。故事情节将逐渐成形。人物弧线也会慢慢发展。而你，将是这一切的背后驱动力。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621900/extras/18c181219589113bebf23ab06ac20dea.poster.avif?t=1765282542\" width=600 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621900/extras/18c181219589113bebf23ab06ac20dea.webm?t=1765282542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1621900/extras/18c181219589113bebf23ab06ac20dea.mp4?t=1765282542\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></